item.title: CVE-2018-5543|2024-08-05T05:40:50.580Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- f5%20container%20connector
item.description: The F5 BIG-IP Controller for Kubernetes 1.0.0-1.5.0 (k8s-bigip-crtl) passes BIG-IP username and password as command line parameters, which may lead to disclosure of the credentials used by the container.
